column10: Drivers speed through this stop sign with no regard to pedestrians. Sometimes even when seen, just swerve around them.
This stop sign is primarily ignored by drivers. This is a very dangerous intersection.

An ongoing problem with cyclists who refuse to stop, or even slow down to yield to adults and children coming and going to school. They become very confrontational if this is brough to their attention. They are breaking the law and should be ticketed.
